Package: RBitly
Type: Package
Title: R Wrapper for the Bit.ly API and Ow.ly
Description: Allows users accessing 'Bit.ly API' http://dev.bitly.com/ and retrieve many useful statistics. Now, additionally supports 'Ow.ly' http://ow.ly/api-docs.
Version: 0.7
Date: 2015-08-21
